view.name: Map of Grocery Stores - 2011
view.description: Contains a list of grocery stores which was used by the city to calculate the estimates of Chicagoans living in food deserts in 2011. Data in this file can be cross-referenced with the city's business license data (http://bit.ly/sMFZdN).

columns.name: STORE NAME
columns.description: Name of the grocery store. This corresponds to the "DOING BUSINESS AS NAME" listed in the business licenses dataset (http://bit.ly/sMFZdN).

top.item: W K R B FOOD & LIQUOR

columns.name: LICENSE ID
columns.description: License ID is the same as the leading portion of the "ID" field (left of the dash) in the business license dataset (http://bit.ly/sMFZdN)

columns.name: SQUARE FEET
columns.description: Square feet of the grocery store.

columns.name: COMMUNITY AREA NAME
columns.description: Name of the community area where grocery store is located

columns.name: COMMUNITY AREA
columns.description: Numerical indicator of the community area.

columns.name: WARD
columns.description: Ward number of where grocery store is located

columns.name: CENSUS TRACT
columns.description: The ID corresponding to the U.S. Census Bureau's tract ID. See http://bit.ly/153StpV for a complete list of Census tracts in Chicago.

columns.name: CENSUS BLOCK
columns.description: The ID corresponding to the U.S. Census Bureau's block ID. See http://bit.ly/15f3FNJ for a complete list of Census blocks in Chicago.

columns.name: X COORDINATE
columns.description: The X coordinate of the store's location using the Illinois-East State Plane Coordinate Projections (http://bit.ly/177plfn)

columns.name: Y COORDINATE
columns.description: The Y coordinate of the store's location using the Illinois-East State Plane Coordinate Projections (http://bit.ly/177plfn)

columns.name: LATITUDE
columns.description: The latitude of the grocery store's location.

columns.name: LONGITUDE
columns.description: The longitude of the grocery store's location.
